Text Only<pre><code> &amp; Provides the address of something stored in memory. //提供地址
  * Instructs the compiler to go to a location in memory. // *让编译器到内存的相应地址
</code></pre> <p>Notice the <code>%p</code>, which allows us to view the address of a location in memory. <code>&amp;n</code> can be literally translated as “the address of <code>n</code>.” Executing this code will return an address of memory beginning with <code>0x</code>.</p> <p><code>%p</code>：返回存储地址，以<code>0x</code>开头</p> Text Only<pre><code>int n = 50;

int *p = &amp;n;
</code></pre> <p>p的性质：指针。可以保存地址。</p> <p><code>p</code> is a pointer that contains the address of an integer <code>n</code>.</p> <p>To illustrate the use of the <code>*</code> operator, consider the following:</p> Text Only<pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;

int main(void)
{
    int n = 50;
    int *p = &amp;n;
    printf("%i\n", *p);
}
</code></pre> <p>Notice that the <code>printf</code> line prints the integer at the location of <code>p</code>. <code>int *p</code> creates a pointer whose job is to store the memory address of an integer.</p> <p>* → go to the specific location &amp; → tell me the location of sth</p> <p>格式代码→%p 可以 get the address</p> <p>string: 字符序列里面第一个字符的地址</p> <p>char *string</p>

Text Only<pre><code>LILY 00001 70
ALICE 00002 59
BOB 00003 68
EVE 00004 59
MALORY 00005 81
ZACK 00006 11
</code></pre> <p>解释：</p> <ul> <li>LILY最终成绩是69.89分左右，舍入到70。</li> <li>ALICE虽然成绩优异，但编程题补考均未全对，算作59分。</li> <li>BOB实验考试参加了补考，调整分数固定为9，取得的满分也无法提高成绩。因为其它分数很优秀，阶段测试缺考并未影响最后及格。</li> <li>EVE理论考试未达到50分，算作59分。</li> <li>MALORY最终成绩是80.5分，刚好卡在0.5，四舍五入到81。</li> <li>ZACK成绩实在太烂，不会因为单项不及格反而提高到59分。</li> </ul> C<pre><code>#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;stdlib.h&gt;
#include &lt;string.h&gt;
#include &lt;stdbool.h&gt;
#include &lt;math.h&gt;
#include &lt;ctype.h&gt;

// 判断字符串是否为数字
bool is_number(char *str) {
    while (*str) {
        if (!isdigit(*str)) {
            return false;
        }
        str++;
    }
    return true;
}

bool judge_pr_failed(char *a, char *b) {
    int a1;
    int b1;
    char *endptr;
    if (is_number(a)) {
        a1 = strtol(a, &amp;endptr, 10);
    } else {
        a1 = 0;
    }
    if (is_number(b)) {
        b1 = strtol(b, &amp;endptr, 10);
    } else {
        b1 = 0;
    }
    if (a1 &lt; 10 &amp;&amp; b1 &lt; 15) { // 使用整数常量进行比较
        return false;
    } else {
        return true;
    }
}

int min(int a, int b) {
    if (a &lt; b) {
        return a;
    } else {
        return b;
    }
}

int main(void) {
    char *lst[10000];
    int i = 0;

    while (i &lt; 10000) {
        char str[256]; // 假设每行最多256个字符
        if (fgets(str, sizeof(str), stdin) == NULL) {
            break;
        }

        // 为当前行分配内存并存储
        lst[i] = malloc(strlen(str) + 1);
        strcpy(lst[i], str);
        i++;
    }

    char *name[i];
    char *id[i];
    char *attendence[i];
    char *homework[i];
    char *quiz[i];
    char *th_test[i];
    char *pr_test1[i];
    char *pr_test2[i];
    char *pr_atest1[i];
    char *pr_atest2[i];
    char *endptr;
    bool pass = true;
    for (int j = 1; j &lt; i; j++) {
        char *rest = lst[j];
        name[j] = strtok(rest, " "); // 获取姓名
        id[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 获取学号 
        attendence[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 考勤成绩 
        homework[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 作业成绩 
        quiz[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 小测成绩
        th_test[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 理论考试成绩
        pr_test1[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 实验考试成绩 1
        pr_test2[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 实验考试成绩 2
        pr_atest1[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 实验补考成绩 1
        pr_atest2[j] = strtok(NULL, " "); // 实验补考成绩 2
    }
    double grade[i];
    int n = 0;
    double Att;
    double Hom;
    double Quiz;
    double Th_test;
    double Pr_test = 0.0;
    for (n = 1; n &lt; i; n++) {
        Att = strtod(attendence[n], &amp;endptr);
        grade[n] = Att;

        Hom = strtod(homework[n], &amp;endptr);
        grade[n] += 0.2 * Hom;

        if (is_number(quiz[n])) {
            Quiz = strtod(quiz[n], &amp;endptr);
            grade[n] += 0.25 * Quiz;
        }



        if (judge_pr_failed(pr_test1[n], pr_test2[n])) {
            pass = true;
            Pr_test += strtod(pr_test1[n], &amp;endptr);
            Pr_test += strtod(pr_test2[n], &amp;endptr);
            Pr_test = 10.0 + sqrt(Pr_test);
            grade[n] += Pr_test; // 第一次就过了，正常计算实验得分
        } else {
            // 第一次没过，需要判断第二次有没有过
            if (judge_pr_failed(pr_atest1[n], pr_atest2[n])) {
                pass = true;
                grade[n] += 9; // 第二次过了，固定是9分
            } else {
                pass = false; // 直接挂科
                if (is_number(pr_test1[n])) {
                    Pr_test += strtod(pr_test1[n], &amp;endptr);
                }
                if (is_number(pr_test2[n])) {
                    Pr_test += strtod(pr_test2[n], &amp;endptr);
                }
                Pr_test = 10.0 + sqrt(Pr_test);
                grade[n] += Pr_test; // 也照样计算实验得分
            }

        }

        Th_test = strtod(th_test[n], &amp;endptr);
        grade[n] += 0.35 * Th_test;
        if (Th_test &lt; 60) {
            pass = false;
        }
        if (pass == false) {
             grade[n] = min(59, (int)grade[n]);
        }

    }

    // 输出
    for (int x = 1; x &lt; i-1; x++) {
        printf("%s %s %.0f\n", name[x], id[x], round(grade[x]));
    }
    printf("%s %s %.0f", name[i-1], id[i-1], round(grade[i-1]));
    // 释放动态分配的内存
    for (int s = 0; s &lt; i; s++) {
        free(lst[s]);
    }

    return 0;
}
